                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4379" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0615</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7955 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">离开，或许只是为了归来——奥普家居弃港投A的奇异之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Leave, Maybe Just to Return ——AUPU Home Style Corporation Limited’s Strange Journey from H Stock Market to A Stock Market</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贾明琪，郭倩楠，周贝贝</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">兰州大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">奥普家居股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">奥普家居；IPO；H股；A股</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">AUPU Home; IPO; H stocks; A stocks</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">奥普家居股份有限公司主要从事浴霸、集成吊顶等家居产品的研发、生产、销售及相关服务提供。2006年12月，奥普家居的原间接控股股东奥普集团曾在香港联交所公开发行股票并上市，后于2016年9月完成退市流程。此后，奥普家居一直保持低调，历经两年蛰伏，奥普家居终于想要再次发力。这一次，这家浴霸行业的领头羊又瞄准了A股市场。然而，市场对于奥普家居的IPO之路争议不断……本案例首先对奥普家居的发展及业务与行业背景进行简述，随后以时间线为基础，先详细分析奥普家居撤离H股及转战A股的原因，后又对奥普家居闯关IPO途中存在的问题进行探讨。希望通过本案例的研究分析，为我国上市企业以及监管机构提供参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">AUPU Home Style Corporation Limited is mainly engaged in the research and development, production, sales and related services of bathroom, integrated ceiling and other household products. In December 2006, AUPU Group, the former indirect controlling shareholder of AUPU Home, had publicly issued shares on the Hong Kong Stock Exchange and listed on the stock exchange. After that, the delisting process was completed in September 2016. Since then, AUPU Home has been keeping a low profile, after two years of dormancy, AUPU Home finally wants to work hard again. This time, the bathroom leader is targeting the A-share market. However, the market for AUPU Home&#39;s IPO road controversy continues... This case first gives a brief description of the development, business and industry background of AUPU Home. Then, based on the time line, the reasons for AUPU Home&#39;s withdrawal from H Stock Market and its transition to A Stock Market are analyzed in detail, and then the problems faced by AUPU Home during its IPO process are discussed. It is hoped that through the case study and analysis, it can provide reference opinions for listed companies and regulators in China.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《IPO财务会计实务与案例分析》、《高级财务会计理论与实务》、《高级财务管理理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司拟 IPO 财务造假</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-03</td>
